column5: Well there were plenty of them, we just couldnt hook them up for some reason.      The ride out was picturastic.          Fishing was nothing like last saturday. Probly due to the 100 boats out there. We stayed our course and finally hooked up.    This one went home, as it took the hook into the gills and got ripped out. Part of the game . Some get released, some come home. Hey look, Im smiling.LOL    Out on the toon in the morning at first light for whities.
yup, bugged the hell out of me
Nice!!!!  The bugs! That almost looks like some snapchat filter hahaha, brutal.  Nice scenery out there! One of these days Ill fish down that way.  Ill be out for walleye and pike again tomorrow
